Interface MapGraph<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type for identifier of the City objects, e.g E is of type Integer; City can be referred to as 1, 2, etc.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EuroMap

    public interface MapGraph<E>
    A Graph to store a Map-like representation containing cities [City] as nodes and roads [Path] as edges.
    Author:
    Zac Hamid - z5059915
    See Also:
    City, Path
